    <p style="text-indent: 40; text-align: justify"><font size="2">83. Graham G., Holt-Hale
    S., McEwen T. &amp; Parker M., 1986. Children moving (2nd ed.). - California: Mayfield
    Publishing.</font></p>
    <p style="text-indent: 40; text-align: justify"><font size="2">84. Handbuch der
    integrativen Erziehung behinderter und nichtbehinderter Kinder. - Munchen, 1990. </font></p>
    <p style="text-indent: 40; text-align: justify"><font size="2">85. Johnson D. &amp;
    Johnson R., 1975. Learning together and alone. - Englewood Cliffs: Prentice-Hall. </font></p>
    <p style="text-indent: 40; text-align: justify"><font size="2">86. Marlow M., 1980 a.
    Games analysis: Designing games for handicapped children // Teaching Exceptional Children,
    12 (1), pp. 48-51. </font></p>
    <p style="text-indent: 40; text-align: justify"><font size="2">87. Marlow M., 1980 b.
